<s> Content that is updated often might not be processed and read in time or in the proper order by an assistive technology or voice browser.  </s>
<s> Examples (informative) Examples of content that requires a response within a timed interval: * automatic refresh, * redirection, * blinking or scrolling text * dialog that disappears after a short period * shutdown or deactivation of page if activity is not received in a set amount of time * Example 1: blinking text.  </s>
