<s> The following are additional ideas for enhancing a site along this particular dimension: Note: Because the form and origin (including letters, art, historical documents, etc) of content varies so greatly, specific criteria for the type and amount of emphasis to be provided can not be standardized.  </s>
<s> Objective success criteria cannot therefore be formulated that would apply across media and documents.  </s>
<s> Advisory recommendations are however listed below to provide guidance in emphasizing the structure of content.  </s>
<s> See also the techniques documents for the different technologies.  </s>
<s> * for visual presentations, use font variations, styles, size and white space to emphasize structure.  </s>
<s> * use color and graphics to emphasize structure.  </s>
<s> * for auditory presentations, use different voice characteristics and/sounds for major headings, sections and other structural elements.  </s>
